# Form Standardization Rule

- Use react-hook-form for non-trivial forms.
- Use zod as the validation source of truth.
- Do not invent a separate internal form framework unless explicitly approved.
- Keep schema logic, submit logic, and field UI separated when complexity grows.
- Standardize error rendering and pending states.